<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport">
    <title>Edit Field Layout</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .nav-group input[type="checkbox"] { display: none; }
        .nav-group input[type="checkbox"]:checked ~ .nav-subitems { display: block; }
        .nav-group input[type="checkbox"]:checked ~ label .nav-chevron { transform: rotate(90deg); }
        .nav-subitems { display: none; }
        .nav-chevron { transition: transform 0.15s ease; display: inline-block; }
        #sidebar-toggle { display: none; }
        #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .app-shell #primary-sidebar { transform: translateX(0); }
        #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .sidebar-overlay { display: block; }
        .drag-handle { cursor: grab; }
        .drag-handle:active { cursor: grabbing; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-100 text-slate-950 antialiased">
<input id="sidebar-toggle" type="checkbox">
<label for="sidebar-toggle" class="sidebar-overlay fixed inset-0 z-20 hidden bg-slate-900/40" aria-hidden="true"></label>
<div class="app-shell min-h-screen lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[17rem_1fr]">
    <aside id="primary-sidebar" class="fixed inset-y-0 left-0 z-30 w-64 -translate-x-full overflow-y-auto border-r border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-6 transition-transform duration-200 lg:relative lg:inset-auto lg:z-auto lg:w-auto lg:translate-x-0 lg:transition-none">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between lg:block"><a class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight" href="#">Admin</a><label for="sidebar-toggle" class="cursor-pointer rounded-md p-1 text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-100 lg:hidden" aria-label="Close menu"><svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg></label></div>
        <nav class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm font-medium lg:mt-8"><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="home.twig">Dashboard</a><div class="nav-group"><input id="nav-content" type="checkbox" checked><label for="nav-content" class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-emerald-700"><span>Content</span><span class="nav-chevron"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span></label><ul class="nav-subitems ml-3 mt-1 space-y-0.5 border-l border-slate-200 pl-3"><li><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="#">Articles</a></li><li><a class="block rounded-md bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1.5 font-semibold text-emerald-700" href="edit-field-layout.twig">Field Layouts</a></li></ul></div><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="#">Settings</a></nav>
    </aside>
    <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 sm:px-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><label for="sidebar-toggle" class="cursor-pointer rounded-md p-1.5 text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-100 lg:hidden" aria-label="Open menu"><svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg></label><div><h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 sm:text-base">Edit Field Layout</h4><nav class="mt-0.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500 sm:text-sm"><a class="hover:text-slate-800" href="#">Dashboard</a><svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg><span class="text-slate-800">Article Layout</span></nav></div></div></div>
        <div class="flex flex-1 gap-6 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[14rem_1fr]">
            <aside class="hidden h-fit lg:block"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Field Layouts</h5></div><nav class="p-2"><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50" href="create-field-layout.twig">New Layout</a><a class="mt-0.5 block rounded-md bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700" href="edit-field-layout.twig">Edit Layout</a><a class="mt-0.5 block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50" href="create-field-layout-tab.twig">New Tab</a><a class="mt-0.5 block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50" href="field-layout-tab-fields.twig">Tab Fields</a></nav></div></aside>
            <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"><div><h1 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-2xl">Article Layout</h1><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Manage tabs and settings for this field layout.</p></div><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><a href="create-field-layout-tab.twig" class="rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-700">Add Tab</a><a href="delete-field-layout.twig" class="rounded-md border border-red-200 bg-red-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-red-700 shadow-sm hover:bg-red-100">Delete</a></div></div>
                <form method="POST" action="#" class="flex flex-col gap-5 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_18rem] lg:items-start">
                    <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-4">
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-3"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Layout Details</h5></div><div class="space-y-4 px-5 py-5"><div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700" for="name">Name</label><input id="name" name="name" value="Article Layout" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-emerald-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20"></div><div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700" for="handle">Handle</label><input id="handle" name="handle" value="article-layout" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-emerald-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20"></div><div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700" for="description">Description</label><textarea id="description" rows="3" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-emerald-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20">Default article editing layout.</textarea></div></div></div>
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-3"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Tabs</h5><span class="text-xs text-slate-400">Drag to reorder</span></div></div><ul id="tabs-list" class="divide-y divide-slate-100">{% set tabs = [{name:'Content',fields:6},{name:'SEO',fields:4},{name:'Advanced',fields:3}] %}{% for tab in tabs %}<li class="tab-row flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3.5 hover:bg-slate-50" data-id="{{ loop.index }}"><span class="drag-handle text-slate-300"><svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6.75h16.5M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 5.25h16.5"/></svg></span><span class="inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">{{ loop.index }}</span><div class="min-w-0 flex-1"><p class="truncate text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">{{ tab.name }}</p><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">{{ tab.fields }} assigned fields</p></div><a href="field-layout-tab-fields.twig" class="rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50">Manage Fields</a></li>{% endfor %}</ul></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-4"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-3"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Save</h5></div><div class="space-y-4 px-5 py-5"><div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Scope</label><select class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-emerald-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20"><option selected>Articles</option><option>Users</option><option>Media</option></select></div><label class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-700"><input type="checkbox" checked class="rounded border-slate-300 text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500"> Active</label></div><div class="space-y-2 border-t border-slate-100 px-5 py-4"><button type="submit" class="w-full rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-700">Save Layout</button><a href="create-field-layout.twig" class="block w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50">Cancel</a></div></div></div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer class="mt-auto border-t border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 sm:px-6"><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">&copy; 2026 Admin &mdash; All rights reserved.</p><nav class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-400"><a class="hover:text-slate-600" href="#">Documentation</a><a class="hover:text-slate-600" href="#">Support</a><a class="hover:text-slate-600" href="#">Privacy</a><span class="text-slate-300">|</span><span>v1.0.0</span></nav></div></footer>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Sortable/1.15.0/Sortable.min.js"></script>
<script>Sortable.create(document.getElementById('tabs-list'), { handle: '.drag-handle', animation: 150 });</script>
</body>
</html>
